    },
    {
      "@id": "sec:md:knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document:mobile-first-responsive-contract:38",
      "@type": "Section",
      "labels": [
        "Section"
      ],
      "name": "Mobile-First Responsive Contract",
      "chunk_text": "Mobile-First Responsive Contract",
      "properties": {
        "heading": "Mobile-First Responsive Contract",
        "level": 2,
        "anchor": "mobile-first-responsive-contract",
        "order": 4
      },
      "metadata": {
        "parsedAt": "2026-05-24T02:20:53+00:00",
        "source": "knowgrph_parser.graph_builder",
        "codebaseRoot": "/Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph",
        "codebaseRelPath": "docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md",
        "documentPath": "docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md",
        "sourceUri": "file:///Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph/docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md",
        "sourcePath": "/Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph/docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md",
        "codebasePath": "docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md#L38",
        "lineStart": 38,
        "lineEnd": 38,
        "sourceSha256": "a3cb877b0e0618f599a0183a99abb3247e5724b921e7792caf2454c113f566cd"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "blk:md:knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document:table:40:1",
      "@type": "Table",
      "labels": [
        "Table"
      ],
      "name": "Table 1",
      "chunk_text": "| Surface | Mobile-First Directive | Forbidden Drift |\n|---------|------------------------|-----------------|\n| MainPanel Integrations | Collapse provider setup into a touch-safe setup flow with reachable inputs, validation states, and actions. | Desktop-only forms, hidden submit actions, route-specific mobile patches |\n| FloatingPanel Chat UI | Stay usable above the virtual keyboard and preserve visible context while tool traces or streamed output update. | Scroll traps, keyboard overlap, unbounded auto-scroll, duplicate chat shells |\n| Editor Workspace | Keep Markdown/source editing reachable with toolbar, touch-sized Markdown/Viewer pane toggles, Explorer, editor panes, Monaco host, textarea fallback, and compact overlay width defaults that prioritize editing while preserving the canoni",
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "| Surface | Mobile-First Directive | Forbidden Drift |\n|---------|------------------------|-----------------|\n| MainPanel Integrations | Collapse provider setup into a touch-safe setup flow with reachable inputs, validation states, and actions. | Desktop-only forms, hidden submit actions, route-specific mobile patches |\n| FloatingPanel Chat UI | Stay usable above the virtual keyboard and preserve visible context while tool traces or streamed output update. | Scroll traps, keyboard overlap, unbounded auto-scroll, duplicate chat shells |\n| Editor Workspace | Keep Markdown/source editing reachable with toolbar, touch-sized Markdown/Viewer pane toggles, Explorer, editor panes, Monaco host, textarea fallback, and compact overlay width defaults that prioritize editing while preserving the canonical canvas gutter. Viewer preview toggles must keep an editable source pane visible. | Overlapping fixed bars, inaccessible editor controls, cramped side-by-side editors, tiny pane checkboxes, preview-only dead ends, local gutter literals, second preview mounts |\n| Toolbar and Same-Row Controls | Scroll horizontally within the active row from shared toolbar row-scroll classes, keep the primary canvas toolbar thumb-reachable inside safe-area bounds on mobile, and keep icon buttons, launch/dropdown menu rows, design controls, settings previews, chips, labels, table tag lists, and data-view actions clipped through one responsive element-row primitive. | Wrapped icon rows, duplicated overflow classes, component-local scroll rules, top-edge-only mobile toolbars |\n| Canvas | Preserve pan, zoom, fit, selection, quick edit, and inspect actions through touch and pointer input. | Component-local breakpoints, hardcoded coordinates, resize-observer loops |\n| Rich Media Panel | Keep media playback, fallback states, and metadata inspection reachable inside safe-area-aware bounds. | Offscreen-only controls, silent clipping, desktop-only playback affordances |\n| Generated Widgets | Emit responsive bounds, min sizes, fit strategy, edge anchors, and overflow behavior as metadata. | One-off fixed scenes, stale desktop coordinates, hidden edge handles |",
        "order": 1
      },
      "metadata": {
        "parsedAt": "2026-05-24T02:20:53+00:00",
        "source": "knowgrph_parser.graph_builder",
        "codebaseRoot": "/Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph",
        "codebaseRelPath": "docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md",
        "documentPath": "docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md",
        "sourceUri": "file:///Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph/docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md",
        "sourcePath": "/Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph/docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md",
        "codebasePath": "docs/documents/knowgrph-ui-ux-design-document.md#L40-48",
        "lineStart": 40,
        "lineEnd": 48,
        "sourceSha256": "a3cb877b0e0618f599a0183a99abb3247e5724b921e7792caf2454c113f566cd"
      }
    },
    {
